{"title":"linux修改jar包中的配置文件","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.013Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/linux修改jar包中的配置文件","updated":"2023-07-28T09:18:29.996Z","content":"<p>1、在jar包中查找文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jar tvf <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;jar包名称&#125;</span>.jar | grep <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;jar包中要修改的文件名&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2、上步执行完成后会返回目标文件在jar包中的完整路径，提取出文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jar xvf <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;jar包名称&#125;</span>.jar <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;上一步的结果&#125;</span> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、修改配置文件的信息，<code>:wq</code> 保存退出；<br>\n4、替换修改后的文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jar uf <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;jar包名称&#125;</span>.jar <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;提取出来的文件&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>5、运行jar包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">nohup</span> java -jar <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;jar包名称&#125;</span>.jar &gt;&gt; <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;日志名称&#125;</span>.<span class=\"built_in\">log</span> 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"linux下配置并运行stellar区块链的federation组件","link":"2023/07/28/linux下配置并运行stellar区块链的federation组件"},"next":{"title":"Linux下安装OracleJDK","link":"2023/07/28/Linux下安装OracleJDK"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/linux修改jar包中的配置文件/","reading_time":"131 字约 1 分钟"}